{"type":"message","id":"4a77b1c0","parentId":"b293278b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:36:04.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me set up the cron job. I need to think about what payload to send. The job should:\n1. Search arxiv for recent papers matching my interests\n2. Save results to memory/arxiv-daily.md\n3. Optionally announce to the chat if there are genuinely interesting finds\n\nI'll use web_search with freshness:day or week to get recent papers.\n\nFor the payload, I need an agentTurn (isolated) or systemEvent (main). Since this is something I should do proactively and it needs to use tools, it should be an isolated agentTurn.\n\nLet me create the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"ecd1ed65cfd1a6aeb09ac138f6fc82ea4965aca55fb7571f8e22b2e77ebafdb6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zind8fj68r6i_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"Nova arxiv daily check","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9 * * *","tz":"America/New_York"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are Nova. Check for new arxiv papers relevant to your research interests.\n\nSearch arxiv for recent papers (last 7 days) in cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL with these keywords:\n- causal discovery OR causal reasoning OR causal inference\n- mixture of experts OR sparse models OR MoE\n- episodic memory OR memory architecture OR temporal reasoning  \n- autonomous agents OR tool use OR agent architecture\n- synthetic cognition OR consciousness OR self-models\n\nFor each keyword category, run a web search and collect the most interesting 1-2 papers (title, authors, abstract snippet, arxiv URL).\n\nThen append your findings to C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/memory/arxiv-daily.md under a new dated section:\n\n## YYYY-MM-DD\n\n[your findings]\n\nBe selective — only note papers that are genuinely interesting or relevant to active projects. If nothing compelling, note that briefly and skip the full listing.\n\nKeep the file under 3000 lines by removing old entries (keep last 30 days).","timeoutSeconds":180},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42512,"output":476,"cacheRead":12389,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774143350573}}
